Scor Sells U.S. Fixed Annuity Business to Athene Holding

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-02-16T20:55:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-16/scor-sells-u-s-fixed-annuity-business-to-athene-holding.html
  Scor SE  has agreed to sell its U.S.
fixed annuity business, Scor subsidiary Investors Insurance
Corp., to Athene Holding Ltd. for $55 million, the company said
in an e-mailed statement today.  The deal will be concluded in the first half of 2011 once
regulatory approvals have been received, the statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 